---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Data scientist, educator, and AI specialist focused on problem-solving and data-driven solutions, with expertise in strategic leadership and educational technology implementation. Currently Data Science Specialist at London School of Economics and Political Science, managing Digital Skills Lab projects, developing Tableau-based reporting systems, and delivering data science training in Python, R, and Tableau. MSc Artificial Intelligence student at University of Leeds with strong background in AI literacy, digital strategy, and educational technology.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="MSc Artificial Intelligence"
      subtitle="2024-2026 (In Progress) at University of Leeds"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Professional Certificate in Machine Learning and AI"
      subtitle="2024 at Imperial College Business School"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Postgraduate Certificate in Digital Education"
      subtitle="2024 at University of Edinburgh"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="PGCE in Physics & Mathematics"
      subtitle="2004 at University of Greenwich, London"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="BSc Hons Physics"
      subtitle="2003 at University College London"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Data Science Specialist, Innovation Evaluation and AI Literacy"
      subtitle="06/2023–Present at London School of Economics and Political Science"
    >
      Manages Digital Skills Lab projects and evaluation metrics. Designs live Tableau reporting for booking data analytics. Delivers Python, R, and Tableau training to learners. Oversees AI Literacy module development.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Freelance Consultant"
      subtitle="03/2023–Present"
    >
      Provides strategy, training, and data analysis for SMEs and business owners. Launches digital products including Learning Management Systems and data visualization tools.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Head of Digital Strategy and Data"
      subtitle="09/2022–03/2023 at Education for the 21st Century"
    >
      Managed digital transition and formative development phases. Designed Data Operating Model and Digital Education Strategy. Developed trust-wide digital skills audit using agile methodologies. Implemented Arbor assessment system.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Digital Learning Lead"
      subtitle="09/2021–08/2022 at Harris Federation"
    >
      Authored Trust digital education strategy. Led Microsoft SharePoint implementation across three schools. Supported Minecraft Education Edition rollout for Key Stage 2 coding.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Digital Innovation & Learning Lead"
      subtitle="09/2019–08/2021 at Star Academies"
    >
      Achieved Microsoft showcase status for EdTech flagship school. Created Star EdTech Toolkit. Project managed Big Teach Event delivering online CPD to 28 schools. Supported remote learning during lockdown.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Head of eLearning"
      subtitle="08/2017–08/2019 at DLD College London"
    >
      Authored digital education strategy and implemented Canvas LMS. Developed custom CPD program (won Alpha Plus Innovation Award). Led teaching-learning community and student Digital Innovators group.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Mathematics & Advanced Skills Teacher"
      subtitle="12/2012–08/2017 at Woodhouse College, London"
    >
      Teaching and curriculum development in mathematics and advanced skills.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li>Microsoft Certified Educator</li>
    <li>Microsoft Office Specialist (Excel and Excel Expert)</li>
    <li>Microsoft Technology Associate (Python)</li>
    <li>Minecraft Global Mentor</li>
    <li>Microsoft Innovative Educator Expert and Master Trainer</li>
    <li>Fellow, Chartered College of Teaching (FCCT)</li>
    <li>Associate Member, Association of Learning Technology (ALT)</li>
    <li>Certified Scrum Master</li>
    <li>Certified TAP Trainer</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-5 columns-2 mx-6">
    <li>Python (Scikit Learn, PyTorch, TensorFlow, NumPy, Pandas, Matplotlib, Seaborn, Skopt)</li>
    <li>R</li>
    <li>Tableau Prep & Desktop</li>
    <li>Data Visualization</li>
    <li>Machine Learning</li>
    <li>Data Analysis & Statistical Analysis</li>
    <li>Microsoft Office Suite</li>
    <li>SharePoint</li>
    <li>GitHub & VS Code</li>
    <li>Asana, MS Project, Jira</li>
    <li>SPSS & GeoGebra</li>
    <li>Canvas LMS & Moodle</li>
    <li>SMART Board</li>
